name: Can You Tap It: Fast Memorize Vehicle Match Puzzle
name_original: Can You Tap It: Fast Memorize Vehicle Match Puzzle
description:
Fast tap right vehicles puzzle is a simple game.
Quickly tap the tile with the right vehicles and don't get confused by the constantly changing vehicles. Get the right vehicles and get the highest score!
There is 3 levels to play : easy,normal,hard, you can start test your reflex and brain now!
